Name: Franky Lettuce
About the game: Help Franky to discover the world and solve hidden puzzles in each level. Escape a factory filled with cardboard boxes, steel constructions and radioactive waste. Relax in the woods, in which you can find mushrooms to jump on and roses that aren't that sociable, or perhaps you prefer to hang out on the beach with some chill hedgehog.
